==Starting off==
===Without the requirements===
* '''Thormac:''' Hello I am Thormac the sorcerer.
* '''Player:''' Do you need anything?
* '''Thormac:''' Not right now, but thank you for offering.
* {{tbox|You do not meet all of the requirements to start the Scorpion Catcher quest.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===With the requirements===
* '''Thormac:''' Hello I am Thormac the sorcerer. I don't suppose you could be of assistance to me?
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|What do you need assistance with?}}
** '''Player:''' What do you need assistance with?
** '''Thormac:''' I've lost my pet scorpions. They're lesser Kharid scorpions, a very rare breed.
** '''Thormac:''' I left their cage door open, now I don't know where they've gone.
** '''Thormac:''' There's three of them, and they're quick little beasties. They're all over Gielinor.
** '''Player:''' How would I go about catching them?
** '''Thormac:''' Well I have a scorpion cage here which you can use to catch them in.
** '''Thormac:''' If you go up to the village of Seers, to the North of here, one of them will be able to tell you where the scorpions are now.
** {{tselect|Start the Scorpion Catcher quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' Okay, I will do it then.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'm not interested.
*** '''Thormac:''' Blast! I suppose I'll have to find someone else then.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I'm a little busy.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm a little busy.
** '''Thormac:''' Fair enough.
** {{tact|end}}

===Subsequent dialogue===
* '''Thormac:''' How goes your quest?
* '''Player:''' I've not caught all the scorpions yet.
* '''Thormac:''' Well remember to go speak to the Seers, North of here, if you need any help.
* {{tact|end}}

==First scorpion==
===Help from a seer===
* '''Seer:''' Many greetings.
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|I need to locate some scorpions.}}
** '''Player:''' I need to locate some scorpions.
** '''Seer:''' Well you have come to the right place. I am a master of animal detection.
** '''Seer:''' Do you need to locate any particular scorpion? Scorpions are a creature somewhat in abundance.
** '''Player:''' I'm looking for some lesser Kharid scorpions. They belong to Thormac the Sorcerer.
** '''Seer:''' Let me look into my looking glass.
** {{mes|The seer produces a small mirror}}
** {{mes|The seer gazes into the mirror}}
** {{mes|The seer smoothes his hair with hand}}
** '''Seer:''' I can see a scorpion that you seek. It would appear to be near some nasty spiders. I can see two coffins there as well.
** '''Seer:''' The scorpion seems to be going through some crack in the wall. It's gone into some sort of secret room.
** '''Seer:''' Well see if you can find that scorpion then, and I'll try and get you some information on the others.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=no|I seek knowledge and power!}}

===Subsequent dialogue===
* '''Seer:''' Many greetings.
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|Where did you say that scorpion was again?}}
** '''Player:''' Where did you say that scorpion was again?
** '''Seer:''' Let me look into my looking glass.
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|quest=no|I seek knowledge and power!}}

===Attempting to pick up the scorpion===
* {{mes|The scorpion stings you!}}

===Using the scorpion cage on the scorpion===
* {{mes|You catch a scorpion!}}

==Second and third scorpions==
===More help from a seer===
* '''Seer:''' Many greetings.
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|I've retrieved the scorpion from near the spiders.}}
** '''Player:''' I've retrieved the scorpion from near the spiders.
** '''Seer:''' Well, I've checked my looking glass. There seems to be a kharid scorpion in a little village in the east, surrounded by lots of uncivilised-looking warriors. Some kind of merchant there seems to have picked it up.
** '''Seer:''' That's all I can tell you about that scorpion.
** '''Player:''' Any more scorpions?
** '''Seer:''' It's good that you should ask. I have information on the last scorpion for you.
** '''Seer:''' It seems to be in some sort of upstairs room. There seems to be some sort of brown clothing lying on a table.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=no|I seek knowledge and power!}}

===Brotherly love===
* '''Peksa:''' Are you interested in buying or selling a helmet?
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|quest=no|I could be, yes.}}
* {{topt|quest=no|No, I'll pass on that.}}
* {{topt|I've heard you have a small scorpion in your possession.}}
** '''Player:''' I've heard you have a small scorpion in your possession.
** '''Peksa:''' Now how could you know about that, I wonder? Mind you, I don't have it anymore.
** '''Peksa:''' I gave it as a present to my brother Ivor when I visited our outpost northwest of Camelot.
** '''Peksa:''' Well, actually I hid it in his bed so it would nip him. It was a bit of a surprise gift.
** {{tact|end}}

